cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with spoken language understanding (SLU) systems. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it involves processing speech signals. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses neural network models for SLU tasks. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as SLU is an important component of many social and information networks.
